# Vercel Environment Variables Example
# 
# Copy these to your Vercel Project Settings > Environment Variables
# For Vercel dashboard: https://vercel.com/dashboard

# Production - API Backend URL (deployed on Railway, Render, or other service)
API_BASE=https://your-backend-url.railway.app

# Note: 
# - Replace "your-backend-url.railway.app" with your actual backend URL
# - For local development, use http://localhost:5000
# - Vercel will provide your deployed frontend URL automatically
